						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="quotetitle">Raiden the Quick wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">apparently the PRG-ROM code gets copied into addresses $8000 - $FFFF.</div><br />No, it's not copied. There is no "copying" involved, the ROM contents are just seen at that location. No copying (can't say that enough).</div>
<br />Unless, of course, your code is running on a PowerPak or a Famicom Disk System RAM cart.</div>

